snippet.title: John van Zyl
snippet.description:
They say a war is not truly over until the last person who fought in it has died.
I make videos about my lifelong interest in Military History and the fascinating story of Africa. Creating content about the experiences of the fighting men of Rhodesia in the hope of capturing their stories for posterity. Many of the great warriors I knew have now passed on and their stories have gone with them. For all of us the clock is ticking and I hope to document as much of this history as I can before it's too late. I feel very blessed to be supported in this adventure by such a lovely bunch of people. THANK YOU from the bottom of heart for making this channel possible!
